long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A sleek and modern startpage designed with a dark glassmorphism style. This startpage includes a multi-engine search bar, customizable shortcuts, a weather widget, a quick notes feature, and a date widget that shows facts and historical events for the current day.
